<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />Into your hands I entrust my spirit;</para>

<para style="q1">you will redeem me, Yahweh, God of trustworthiness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />I hate those who serve worthless idols,</para>

<para style="q1">but I trust in Yahweh.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />I will be glad and rejoice in your covenant faithfulness,</para>

<para style="q1">for you saw my affliction;</para>

<para style="q1">you knew the distress of my soul.</para>
